Name[ja]=Copy That でコピー
Name[de]=Mit Copy That kopieren
Name[fr]=Copier avec Copy That
Name[ko]=Copy That로 복사
Name[it]=Copia con Copy That
Name[tr]=Copy That ile kopyala
Name[vi]=Sao chép bằng Copy That
Name[pl]=Kopiuj za pomocą Copy That
Name[nl]=Kopiëren met Copy That
Name[id]=Salin dengan Copy That
Name[uk]=Копіювати через Copy That
Exec=copythat --enqueue copy %F
Icon=copythat

